🎯 STEP 4: Categorization
Your app then converts that probability to a risk category:
if prob >= 0.6:  High Risk
elif prob >= 0.3: Moderate Risk
else: Low Risk

✅ Example: 0.52 → “Moderate Stroke Risk”

